<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西走了一步。砰！她撞到了镜子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有镜子里的自己都在揉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！我被困在大型镜子迷宫里了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，说得对！” 杰克·哈默出现在镜子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！罗西的眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！砰 ！激光从镜子上反射回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当激光经过罗西的头顶时，她躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克·哈默哈哈大笑。“火箭女孩儿，再见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西不停地撞到镜子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟过去了，她还在迷宫里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么才能从这里出去呢？” 罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很快有了主意。她吹了一口冷气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镜子上结满了霜，随后出现了裂缝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，咔嚓！镜子碎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到了出口的标志。“太棒了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当罗西赶到美罗城小学的时候，学校里空荡荡的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给特勒尔打了个电话，然后用超级听力听到了铃声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向铃声跑去，叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手机在他们教室，在特勒尔的包里，但是特勒尔不在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在学校里一边到处走，一边用她的超级听力去听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到了体育馆下面有人说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用手劈开地板，发现在地板下面有一个巨大的漏斗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳进去，沿着一条又长又弯的滑梯滑了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最下方有一个巨大的房间，所有人都被困在了里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！” 潘校长擦了擦额头，“你终于找到我们了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把所有的人都带到安全的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我得找到杰克·哈默。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在学校找到了那个建筑工人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在把学校的电脑往面包车上搬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“住手！” 罗西大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“才不呢！” 杰克·哈默对着罗西开了一钉枪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 罗西的眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克·哈默躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>激光被安全帽弹开，射碎了玻璃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！” 坏人钻进面包车里逃走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西追上了他，跟着面包车飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西使用了她的热感视力。面包车的门熔化了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！” 杰克·海默大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的眼睛发射的激光击破了轮胎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面包车滑进水坑，停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克·哈默想要打开车门。“天啊！我......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“被困住了！” 罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把杰克·哈默送进了监狱，然后去了杰克·哈默的大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>被偷来的东西都在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，她回到了学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“室内休息怎么样啊？” 罗西问朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常好！” 玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！” 杰克说，“体育馆下面有个大滑梯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和特勒尔飞快地看了对方一眼，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>